## Limitations

The findings are limited by the availability of sources and the scope of the search. The discussion is primarily based on philosophical interpretations, which can be subjective and vary widely. Additionally, the search did not include empirical studies or data-driven analyses, which could provide a different perspective on the impact of moral rules on personal freedom.